wifi.DESC:
Simple App to find passwords of your known WiFi networks that you connected to before in only 2 mouse clicks, instead of the other complex ways. And there's a button to copy the password directly.<pre><code class='code-snippet java'>private void refresh() {

    if (osName.startsWith("Windows"))
        refreshInWindows();

    else if (osName.equals("Linux"))
        refreshInLinux();

    fillNetworks(listOfNetworks);

}</code></pre>This method refresh the Wi-Fi networks then update the list.
